Package com.otabi.jcodroneedu

Class InventoryManager

java.lang.Object
com.otabi.jcodroneedu.InventoryManager
public class InventoryManager extends Object
Manages and stores inventory data from the drone and controller. This class acts as a cache for flight statistics, device information, CPU IDs, and addresses. It is populated by the Receiver as messages are parsed from the drone.

Inventory data includes:

  • Count Data: Flight time, takeoff/landing/accident counts
  • Information Data: Device models and firmware versions
  • CPU ID Data: Unique CPU identifiers for drone and controller
  • Address Data: Communication addresses for drone and controller
Since:
1.0.0
